Magic the Gathering: offline card trader for Android.

The application does not require internet access.

Trade cards with your friends using the price list extracted from the MOTL 
website (Magic Online Trading League):

http://classic.magictraders.com/pricelists/

The application is updated oftenly to keep the price list up-to-date.

Features:

- easy to use
- offline search
- open source
- free (really!)
    - no restrictions
    - no ads

Please, feel free to send us feedback:

droid.in.the.sky@gmail.com

The source code is available in GitHub:

https://github.com/droid-in-the-sky/mtg-trader

keywords: magic, mtg, cards, trade, offline
